#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.dict.remove.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.dict.remove"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.dict_.remove.series_dict_remove:1 of
msgid "Remove the item by the key from each dict of the Series."
msgstr "从 Series 的每个字典中根据键删除项。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.dict_.remove.series_dict_remove of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.dict_.remove.series_dict_remove:3 of
msgid "The key to remove, must be in the same key type of the dict."
msgstr "要删除的键，必须与字典中的键类型相同。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.dict_.remove.series_dict_remove:5 of
msgid ""
"When the ``query_key`` is not in the dict, if ``ignore_key_error`` is "
"True, nothing will happen in the dict. If ``ignore_key_error`` is "
"``False``, an ``KeyError`` will be raised. If the dict is ``None``, "
"returns ``None``."
msgstr ""
"当 ``query_key`` 不在字典中时，如果 ``ignore_key_error`` 为 True，则字典"
"中不会发生任何变化。如果 ``ignore_key_error`` 为 ``False``，则会抛出 ``"
"KeyError``。如果字典为 ``None``，则返回 ``None``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.dict_.remove.series_dict_remove of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.dict_.remove.series_dict_remove:10 of
msgid "A Series with the same data type. If the dict is ``None``."
msgstr "具有相同数据类型的 Series。如果字典为 ``None``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.dict_.remove.series_dict_remove of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.dict_.remove.series_dict_remove of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.dict_.remove.series_dict_remove:13 of
msgid ""
"If the ``query_key`` is not in one dict and ``ignore_key_error`` is "
"``False``."
msgstr "如果 ``query_key`` 不在某个字典中且 ``ignore_key_error`` 为 ``False``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.dict_.remove.series_dict_remove:16 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.dict_.remove.series_dict_remove:17 of
msgid "Create a series with dict type data."
msgstr "创建一个包含字典类型数据的 Series。"

